    "“If you're suggesting that we escalate this from a verbal exchange to a physical one, I accept.” – Alhaitham",
    "“I don't need to fight I only need to think. Everything is connected. All I have to do is find the weakest link, deal with the causal factors and everything else tends to resolve itself. Essentially, more time on contemplation, less time on execution.” – Alhaitham",
    "“All intellectuals are lunatics in the eyes of fools. I'll take that as a compliment.” – Alhaitham",
    "“Those who understand the rules can delineate boundaries, and identify gray areas.” – Alhaitham",
    "“To achieve this impossible task, it sounds like you'll need to fool your own heart first. Although it may feel like a trick, self-encouragement may be the most important tool we have.” – Alhaitham",
    "“Naturally, I slept just fine. After all, a good rest should be considered part of the plan, since energy is an important resource.” – Alhaitham",
    "“There is always an opportunity for safety after danger passes.” – Alhaitham",
    "“The Eremites once said that I was a lunatic. Perhaps a little madness is essential to be successful in research.” – Alhaitham",
    "“If you want to raise a vicious wolf, you need to make sure that you can avoid its bite.” – Alhaitham",
    "“The point of discussion is to arrive at a solution. Let's cut the small talk and move to the next point.” – Alhaitham",
    "“When you are unable to understand a reasearcher's actions, most cases can be attributed to curiosity.” – Alhaitham",
    "“Have I ever failed to follow through on my word in the past?” – Alhaitham",
    "“It's crucial to dissipate any tension before we execute our plan.” – Alhaitham",
    "“After all, there will always be those in this world who are dissatisfied with life as designed for them by the Akasha, and wish to change their fate.” – Alhaitham",
    "“Observation is the first step of any experiment, but observing the current world doesn't satisfy me. It lacks an important dimension - that of time.” – Il Dottore",
    "“Even the God of Wisdom is restricted by the habits of cognition. How disappointing.” – Il Dottore",
    "“Oh, no. I certainly have my own convictions. They just don't fit your standards, that's all.” – Il Dottore",
    "“The world is full of lost ballads just waiting to be rediscovered.” – Venti",
    "“Let us make music, not war, and resolve our conflicts through song.” – Venti",
    "“May the winds bless your travels!” – Venti",
    "“Many mortals fear lightning... incomprehensible. Fear of something so common.” – Xiao",
    "“Reduced to just standing around. How absurd.” – Xiao",
    "“Once the snow is thick enough, we can eat it.” – Xiao",
    "“If you awake to a knife at your throat, if monsters dig their claws into you, if death comes knocking at your door, call out my name. Adeptus Xiao. I will be here when you call.” – Xiao",
    "“A warrior must always be ready to face any challenge with his blade. The outcome of the battle is irrelevant - what matters is that you learn from the experience.” – Childe",
    "“Comrade. Make sure you keep training too. Otherwise, who will be left to fight me to the death when the world lies defeated at my feet?” – Tartaglia",
    "“A warrior's strength is like a dome. The bigger the dome, the more opponents he can challenge inside it.” – Childe",
    "“Where I'm from, if we didn't keep moving, we'd freeze to death. Literally.” – Childe",
    "“The rules of war are woven in the womb: the victors shall burn bright, while the losers must turn to ash.” – Dainsleif",
    "“The God of Contracts, senselessly slaughtered as his people watched on in horror. In the end, he will sign the contract to end all contracts.” – Dainsleif",
    "“Now, you who has set foot in this world. \nYour journey has reached its end, but one final doorway remains. \nStep forth, if you have understood the meaning of your journey. \nDefeat me, command me to step aside, show me that you are worthier than I to rescue her. \nThen, the threads of all fate will be yours to re-weave. \nMy memory has all but faded completely... but I will always remember how much she too, loved these flowers.” – Dainsleif",
    "“Sometimes, hopes and dreams bring suffering instead of happiness.” – Kaveh",
    "“The ability to appreciate beauty is an important virtue.” – Kaveh",
    "“If you ask me, I think the people spreading rumors around here don't have access to any real information.” – Kaveh",
    "“I don't understand why people insist on going all out to try and prove how their existence is more valuable than everyone else's. To exist in the first place is a beautiful thing, and that's enough... isn't it?” – Ganyu",
    "“Respect must be given to the will of every creature. Each fish in the ocean swims in its own direction.” – Kokomi",
    "“When small fish gather together, they can act as one body for the protection of all. This is how the weak mount their resistance.” – Kokomi",
    "“Fate had other ideas in store... you can't defy that which flows in your veins.” – Kokomi",
    "“It's said that the depths of a person's heart run deep indeed.” – Kokomi",
