    "“Our work will not handle itself... but, I suppose the occasional short break is warranted. Let us rest for a couple of minutes.” – Jean",
    "“Don't be too ready to believe people when they cross their heart and hope to die. Sweet talkers only say what you want to hear. And think twice before meeting someone else's gaze - your eyes speak volumes about what you're thinking.” – Yelan",
